# TZ-95 — Brutalist Architectural UI Refinement: Phase 3 (Showcase & Docs)

**Дата:** 2026-07-11
**Статус:** ✅ DONE (kit pages + doc files updated, typecheck 0 errors)
**Тип:** cross-cutting (kit showcase + docs sync)
**Приоритет:** высокий (final phase of TZ-93/94/95 brutalist architectural refinement)
**Phases:** 3/3 — финальная phase из 3-фазного плана. Phase 1 = TZ-93 ✅ DONE, Phase 2 = TZ-94 ⏳.
**LAYER:** Phase 3 = **Layer 1** (CSS only + docs — no TS changes, no component API changes)
**Зависимости:** TZ-93 ✅ DONE (3 utilities), TZ-94 ⏳ (component adopters), Paper & Ink design system

**CONFLICT KEYS:**
  - frontend/src/app/pages/foundations/foundations.page.ts            # + new "Pi-* Utilities" section (5th section)
  - frontend/src/app/pages/forms/forms.page.ts                        # + pi-dashed-panel + pi-corner-marks demos in form sections
  - frontend/src/app/pages/overlays/overlays.page.ts                  # + pi-corner-marks + pi-dashed-panel for empty states
  - frontend/src/app/pages/playground/theme-editor.page.ts            # + new "Architectural Patterns" section (Section IV)
  - frontend/src/app/pages/playground/code-preview.page.ts            # + code snippet examples for pi-* utilities
  - docs/paper-and-ink.md                                             # + new "Pi-* Utilities" section
  - docs/add-new-page.md                                              # + "When to use pi-* utilities vs hairline" convention

**Решения пользователя (зафиксированы):**
1. ✅ **Scope**: showcase 4 kit pages (foundations, forms, overlays, playground) + 2 doc files. No new components, no new utilities.
2. ✅ **Layer 1 trivial**: additive content only (new sections, new demos, new doc sections). No breaking changes.
3. ✅ **Doc sections**: add "Pi-* Utilities" section to paper-and-ink.md + "Convention" note to add-new-page.md.
4. ✅ **Kit sections**: 1 new section per page (5 sections total across 4 pages). No existing sections restructured.
5. ✅ **Auth wall**: browser-use visual verify BLOCKED until TZ-93.1 (or this TZ's optional resolution) lands. Typecheck + manual code review is the primary verification gate.

---

## 1. Цель

Showcase the 3 TZ-93 utilities (`.pi-tech-label`, `.pi-corner-marks`, `.pi-dashed-panel`) + the TZ-94 component adoptions (PiEmptyState, PiEmptyTile, PiBadge, PiTable, PiLabel, PiFormField) in the `/kit/*` pages, and canonize the patterns in the Paper & Ink design system docs.

**Что делаем:**
- **Kit showcase**: 4 pages get 1 new section each demonstrating the architectural patterns. All sections are additive (no existing content removed/restructured).
- **Docs sync**: `paper-and-ink.md` gets a new "Pi-* Utilities" section explaining the 3 utilities, their use cases, and the rejected brutalist alternatives. `add-new-page.md` gets a "Convention" note on when to use `pi-*` utilities vs `hairline` borders.
- **Cross-references**: all kit sections link to the docs sections, and vice versa.

**Что НЕ делаем:**
- ❌ New components or utilities.
- ❌ Refactoring existing kit sections.
- ❌ Auth wall resolution (separate TZ-93.1, optional to fold in here).
- ❌ Visual regression testing (browser-use blocked by auth — manual code review + typecheck only).

