## 7. What is NOT in this TZ (explicit deferrals)

- ❌ **TZ-93.1 (auth wall resolution)** — separate TZ to expose `/kit/*` and `/playground/*` as public routes. **OPTIONAL**: if the user wants visual verify to work, fold this into TZ-95 as an additional commit.
- ❌ **TZ-94 component implementation** — TZ-95 is a Layer 1 doc + showcase update. TZ-94 (component refactors) is a separate Phase 2.
- ❌ **New components or utilities** — TZ-95 uses only the 3 TZ-93 utilities + existing components.
- ❌ **Refactoring existing kit sections** — strict additive scope.
- ❌ **Operational page migration** — `/materials`, `/organizations`, `/dictionaries` etc. continue to use the pre-TZ-94 component defaults. Migration to TZ-94 adoptions is a separate effort.
- ❌ **axe-core a11y audit** — separate TZ after the brutalist refinement is complete.

